Kabbalah, the more I

00:01:07.970 --> 00:01:11.320 align:middle line:84%
am able to discover through
the "Sepher Yetzirah."

00:01:11.320 --> 00:01:14.090 align:middle line:84%
But at first, it
was such an enigma--

00:01:14.090 --> 00:01:17.220 align:middle line:90%
a perplexing mystery.

00:01:17.220 --> 00:01:19.350 align:middle line:84%
I'm someone who likes
to solve riddles.

