revealed within this "Sepher

00:01:36.270 --> 00:01:38.170 align:middle line:90%
Yetzirah."

00:01:38.170 --> 00:01:40.720 align:middle line:90%
So what's it revealing to us?

00:01:40.720 --> 00:01:44.470 align:middle line:84%
Well it's formulas for how to
apply these mysteries in a very

00:01:44.470 --> 00:01:47.110 align:middle line:90%
magical way in our lives.

00:01:47.110 --> 00:01:48.820 align:middle line:84%
For me personally,
it was like getting

00:01:48.820 --> 00:01:51.980 align:middle line:84%
